---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import MainCard from "@/components/MainCard.astro";
import Card from "@/components/temple/Card.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <MainCard
    title="About LMF"
    description="一个把旧博客收束进新结构里的个人站点，先站稳，再继续长。"
    image="/images/legacy/wing.PNG"
    infoIcon="lucide:user-round"
  >
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-base-content/80">
          这个站现在已经从旧博客迁到 Astro + Frosti。
          目前迁过来的核心内容不多，主要是友链和一批原来文章里用过的图片资源。
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">
          这么做不是因为以后只会放轻内容，而是想先把底座换成更适合长期写作和整理的结构。
          后面无论是长文、笔记、归档还是更完整的页面，都可以继续往上长。
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <Card>
          <div class="space-y-3 p-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
              <Icon name="lucide:layout-template" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Current shape</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-base-content/75">
              <li>Frosti theme for the overall layout and interaction.</li>
              <li>GitHub Pages deployment kept on the existing repository pipeline.</li>
              <li>Migrated friend links and legacy images preserved under <code>/public/images/legacy</code>.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card>
          <div class="space-y-3 p-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
              <Icon name="lucide:rocket" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Next step</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-base-content/75">
              <li>Keep writing into the new blog content collection.</li>
              <li>Continue refining the site voice and page mix over time.</li>
              <li>Use the cleaner structure as the default place for heavier future content.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </MainCard>
</BaseLayout>
